title: Complete the Square
text: Group and factor: $$4\left(x^2+10x\right)$$ + $$\operatorname{25}\left(y^2-4y\right)$$ $$=$$ $$-100$$. Then complete the square.

title: Divide to Get Standard Form
text: After completing the square: $$\frac{\left(x+5\right)^2}{9}$$ + $$\frac{\left(y-2\right)^2}{4}$$ $$=$$ $$1$$. Identify a $$=$$ $$3$$, $$b$$ $$=$$ $$2$$.
